@NODE Philosophies "Philosophies"

 PHILOSOPHIES
 ------------

  I personally think that basically the human race is good - but there are
  plenty of bad people out there just waiting for a chance to use your va-
  luable text files for their immoral purposes. :-) There can also be some
  texts that you wouldn't like even your closest friend to read.  You have
  the answer for your problems here, Protco is a simple utility especially
  written for crypting text files with several different methods - you can
  also use combinations of these methods for maximum security.

 @{" Return " link Main}

@ENDNODE

@NODE Using "Using Protco"

 USING PROTCO
 ------------

  Using Protco is rather simple, just enter the name of file to be crypted
  to the text gadget or if you have KS2 just press the USE ASL and reques-
  ter should appear.  Then select the most convenient method to crypt your
  precious file with the CHANGE METHOD gadget and then press CODE FILE.

  Uncrypting files is just as simple as crypting, just select the file and
  crypt it again with the same method and it's uncrypted. If you have used
  combinations, just select all the methods backwards.

  The methods can also be selected from a pull-down menu and with keyboard
  shortcuts, currently there are ten available methods for crypting.

 @{" Return " link Main}

@ENDNODE

@NODE Tech "Tech Notes"

 TECH NOTES
 ----------

  o Some crypting methods only work with files longer than 8 bytes, remem-
    ber always to check that the file really was crypted.

